{"asset_id":"candidate_content_method_boundary_v0_5_02","asset_key":"candidate.method_boundary.scoring_layers_explained.v0_5","asset_version":"v0_5","asset_type":"method_boundary","asset_layer":"L0_governance","module_key":"module_10_method_privacy","section_key":"method_privacy","slot_key":"module_10_method_privacy.method.score_method","copy_role":"user_visible_method_boundary_candidate","reading_mode":["standard","deep"],"title_zh":"从回答到五维结构","body_zh":"大五测评会把用户的回答放进一个固定的特质结构里阅读。有些题目从正向观察某个倾向，有些题目从相反方向校正同一类倾向，目的是减少单一作答习惯对结果的影响。细分面向先被整理出来，同一维度下的面向再合并，形成五个维度的结构。这样得到的是一组倾向线索，不是一句即时评价。\n\n边界：这套方法能支持自我理解和行为观察，不能单独证明能力、健康状态、工作表现或未来结果。","short_body_zh":"报告不是把某一句回答直接翻译成评价，而是先形成细分面向，再汇总成五个大维度。","cta_zh":"如果某个维度让你意外，别急着否定。先看它下面的细分面向，再想一个最近发生过的例子。","applies_to":{"scale_code":["BIG5_OCEAN"],"candidate_stage":["method_boundary_v0_5_normalized"],"target_registry_key":["method_registry"],"target_module":["module_10_method_privacy"],"selection_scope":["scoring_method_brief"],"candidate_replaces":["asset.module_10_method_privacy.method_registry.score_method.v0_3"],"original_reading_modes":["standard","deep"]},"avoid_when":[{"field":"runtime_use","operator":"not_equals","value":"staging_only","action":"block_runtime_use"},{"field":"production_use_allowed","operator":"not_equals","value":false,"action":"block_production_use"}],"can_combine_with":["method_registry"],"cannot_combine_with":["runtime_use","production_use","frontend_copy"],"dedupe_group":"method_boundary_v0_5.module_10_method_privacy.method.score_method","selection_priority":93,"selection_specificity":10,"fallback_allowed":false,"render_surface":[],"body_quality":{"body_chars":258,"sentence_count":5,"has_trait_layer":true,"has_score_band_layer":false,"has_coupling_layer":false,"has_facet_layer":true,"has_real_world_layer":true,"has_cost_layer":false,"has_strength_layer":false,"has_action_layer":true,"has_boundary_layer":true,"has_editorial_leakage":false,"template_risk":"v0_5_human_review_candidate","rendered_preview_required":true},"safety_tags":["method_boundary","human_reviewed_candidate","staging_only","not_runtime","no_frontend_copy","no_production_use"],"qa_status":"safety_reviewed","ready_for_pilot":false,"runtime_use":"staging_only","production_use_allowed":false,"source_trace":{"source_pack":"big5_method_boundary_candidates_v0_5.zip","source_zip_sha256":"f69a85caba09654d9774d396a1bf785e2d6f0a26c652026f858422553aebd461","source_role":"citation_only","derived_from":["GPT v0.5 method/boundary candidate workpack","existing_big5_result_page_v2_asset_packs"],"candidate_replaces":["asset.module_10_method_privacy.method_registry.score_method.v0_3"],"forbidden_copy_sources_excluded":true,"bfi_2_copy_used":false,"competitor_copy_used":false,"runtime_use":"staging_only","production_use_allowed":false},"repair_log_refs":[]}
{"asset_id":"candidate_content_method_boundary_v0_5_03","asset_key":"candidate.method_boundary.band_ranges_not_cutoffs.v0_5","asset_version":"v0_5","asset_type":"method_boundary","asset_layer":"L0_governance","module_key":"module_10_method_privacy","section_key":"method_privacy","slot_key":"module_10_method_privacy.method.score_band_boundary","copy_role":"user_visible_method_boundary_candidate","reading_mode":["standard","deep"],"title_zh":"区间是读法，不是判决","body_zh":"报告会把连续分布上的位置转换成更容易读懂的区间。区间的作用是降低理解成本：让你知道某个倾向大致偏突出、偏克制，还是处在中间地带。它不是天然分界线，更不是判决书。尤其在靠近边界的位置，细微差异不应该被读成完全不同的人格结论。\n\n边界：区间不能用于判断一个人好不好、正不正常、有没有能力，或是否适合被录用、淘汰、比较。","short_body_zh":"分档只是帮助阅读倾向强弱的区间语言，不是能力、价值或健康状态的判断。","cta_zh":"阅读区间时，只问一个问题：这个倾向在什么场景里帮到我，什么场景里需要补位？","applies_to":{"scale_code":["BIG5_OCEAN"],"candidate_stage":["method_boundary_v0_5_normalized"],"target_registry_key":["method_registry"],"target_module":["module_10_method_privacy"],"selection_scope":["score_band_boundary"],"candidate_replaces":["asset.module_10_method_privacy.method_registry.score_method.v0_3"],"original_reading_modes":["standard","deep"]},"avoid_when":[{"field":"runtime_use","operator":"not_equals","value":"staging_only","action":"block_runtime_use"},{"field":"production_use_allowed","operator":"not_equals","value":false,"action":"block_production_use"}],"can_combine_with":["method_registry"],"cannot_combine_with":["runtime_use","production_use","frontend_copy"],"dedupe_group":"method_boundary_v0_5.module_10_method_privacy.method.score_band_boundary","selection_priority":92,"selection_specificity":10,"fallback_allowed":false,"render_surface":[],"body_quality":{"body_chars":233,"sentence_count":5,"has_trait_layer":false,"has_score_band_layer":true,"has_coupling_layer":false,"has_facet_layer":false,"has_real_world_layer":false,"has_cost_layer":false,"has_strength_layer":false,"has_action_layer":true,"has_boundary_layer":true,"has_editorial_leakage":false,"template_risk":"v0_5_human_review_candidate","rendered_preview_required":true