{"asset_id":"candidate_content_method_boundary_v0_5_06","asset_key":"candidate.method_boundary.norm_three_state_reading.v0_5","asset_version":"v0_5","asset_type":"norms_explanation","asset_layer":"L0_governance","module_key":"module_10_method_privacy","section_key":"method_privacy","slot_key":"module_10_method_privacy.method.norm_method","copy_role":"user_visible_method_boundary_candidate","reading_mode":["standard","deep"],"title_zh":"参照有三种读法","body_zh":"结果中的相对参照不是永远同一种强度。第一种情况是参照充分，报告可以更稳地解释某个倾向在样本中的位置。第二种情况是参照有限，报告可以保留方向判断，但要弱化精确比较。第三种情况是暂无可靠参照，此时仍可以读五维结构、细分面向和场景建议，但不应把结果读成群体排名。\n\n边界：参照不足时，不能使用精确比较、优劣暗示或曲线式排名来增强说服力。","short_body_zh":"有稳定参照时可以谨慎理解相对位置；参照有限或缺失时，应回到特质结构本身。","cta_zh":"看到参照提示时，先确认这份报告是在讲“我自己的倾向结构”，还是在讲“我与某个群体的相对位置”。","applies_to":{"scale_code":["BIG5_OCEAN"],"candidate_stage":["method_boundary_v0_5_normalized"],"target_registry_key":["method_registry"],"target_module":["module_10_method_privacy"],"selection_scope":["norm_three_state_boundary"],"candidate_replaces":["asset.module_10_method_privacy.method_registry.norm_method.v0_3"],"original_reading_modes":["standard","deep"]},"avoid_when":[{"field":"runtime_use","operator":"not_equals","value":"staging_only","action":"block_runtime_use"},{"field":"production_use_allowed","operator":"not_equals","value":false,"action":"block_production_use"}],"can_combine_with":["method_registry"],"cannot_combine_with":["runtime_use","production_use","frontend_copy"],"dedupe_group":"method_boundary_v0_5.module_10_method_privacy.method.norm_method","selection_priority":89,"selection_specificity":10,"fallback_allowed":false,"render_surface":[],"body_quality":{"body_chars":250,"sentence_count":5,"has_trait_layer":false,"has_score_band_layer":false,"has_coupling_layer":false,"has_facet_layer":true,"has_real_world_layer":true,"has_cost_layer":false,"has_strength_layer":false,"has_action_layer":true,"has_boundary_layer":true,"has_editorial_leakage":false,"template_risk":"v0_5_human_review_candidate","rendered_preview_requir