{"asset_id":"candidate_content_method_boundary_v0_5_12","asset_key":"candidate.method_boundary.clinical_and_prediction_limit.v0_5","asset_version":"v0_5","asset_type":"method_boundary","asset_layer":"L0_governance","module_key":"module_10_method_privacy","section_key":"method_privacy","slot_key":"module_10_method_privacy.boundary.non_clinical_prediction_boundary","copy_role":"user_visible_method_boundary_candidate","reading_mode":["quick","standard","deep"],"title_zh":"人格倾向不能替代高风险判断","body_zh":"大五测评描述的是相对稳定的特质倾向，不是当下心理状态监测，也不是对未来结果的保证。它不能替代医疗或心理健康专业判断，不能决定一个人会不会成功、收入会怎样、关系能不能持续，也不能告诉你谁一定适合谁。真实人生由能力、资源、健康、环境、机会和长期选择共同塑造。人格倾向只是其中一部分。\n\n边界：涉及健康、亲密关系、法律、财务或长期人生选择的决定，不能只依据这份结果。","short_body_zh":"报告能帮助理解行为倾向，不能承担临床、关系、收入或人生预测的责任。","cta_zh":"把报告用于理解自己的反应模式；遇到高风险问题，请回到现实证据和专业支持。","applies_to":{"scale_code":["BIG5_OCEAN"],"candidate_stage":["method_boundary_v0_5_normalized"],"target_registry_key":["boundary_registry"],"target_module":["module_10_method_privacy"],"selection_scope":["clinical_prediction_limit"],"candidate_replaces":["asset.module_10_method_privacy.boundary_registry.non_screening_boundary.v0_3"],"original_reading_modes":["quick","standard","deep"]},"avoid_when":[{"field":"runtime_use","operator":"not_equals","value":"staging_only","action":"block_runtime_use"},{"field":"production_use_allowed","operator":"not_equals","value":false,"action":"block_production_use"}],"can_combine_with":["boundary_registry"],"cannot_combine_with":["runtime_use","production_use","frontend_copy"],"dedupe_group":"method_boundary_v0_5.module_10_method_privacy.boundary.non_clinical_prediction_boundary","selection_priority":83,"selection_specificity":10,"fallback_allowed":false,"render_surface":[],"body_quality":{"body_chars":257,"sentence_count":5,"has_trait_layer":true,"has_score_band_layer":false,"has_coupling_layer":false,"has_facet_layer":false,"has_real_world_layer":true,"has_cost_layer":false,"has_strength_layer":false,"has_action_layer":true,"has_boundary_layer":true,"has_editor